[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "3986021654722714881",
		"text": "亜空間旅行、終点です",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00602",
		"still_path_hash": "4227931788932007159",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "な、なんだと……！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_042_01510",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "このような、ことが……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_00603",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "私たちの力、思い知ったか！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00604",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "場をあれだけ有利に整えて、薄氷を踏む勝利……\nある意味、兄上との実力差を思い知らされた",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_037_00605",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "う～～～",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_00606",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "わ、ゼロ姉貴、起きちゃうかも！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_00607",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "ぐが……すぴー……すぴー……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_00608",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "疲れて、本格的に寝入ったみたいだね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_00609",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "まさか、アタシたちがゼロ姉に勝てるとはね。\n絶対の強さを誇る、０のゼロ姉に",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_00610",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "私たちが勝ったのはみんなで力で合わせたから。\nお互いを信じて、託し合えたからよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00611",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "はは、そうさね。\nゼロ姉が起きたら聞かせてやってくれよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_00612",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "ゼロ姉貴、すっごく気持ちよさそうに寝てる……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_00613",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "やれやれ、寝てるときだけはかわいいもんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_00614",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "3986021654722714881",
		"text": "ゼロはひとまず大丈夫でしょ、次はこっち",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00615",
		"still_path_hash": "4227931788932007159",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "ありえん……人類の管理者たる俺が……\n英雄である俺が、人に負けるなど……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_00616",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "敗因……はさっきアルビーナが言ったでしょ。\n敗者の運命、受け入れてもらう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00617",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "くっ……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_00618",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "な……！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_00619",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "どう？　暴力を振るわれる側になった気持ちは。\nあんたはこれまで、こんな風に相手を支配していたの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00620",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "支配……？　違う。\n俺は上位存在として、兄として、すべきことを――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_00621",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "力と権力をかさに、わがまま三昧。\n自覚もないのがたちが悪いわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00622",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "あんたの力は全知全能なんかじゃない。\nだって、あんたもパルメ族に「管理」されているでしょ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00623",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "俺が、「管理」される側……？\n管理者では、なかったのか……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_00624",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "何度でも言います。私たちに管理は必要ありません。\nもちろん、自分の考えが甘いことは分かっています",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00625",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "でも……しょせん理想論だとしても、最初から\n理想を目指して進まないで、どうするんですか！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00626",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "レスナちゃんだけじゃ心配なところは\nアタシとハンマーがついてる！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_037_00627",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "一人ではなく、多くの者が支え合って進む。\nそれを体現した諸島同盟の平和を知ってるはずだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_037_00628",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "……俺は、負けたんだ。\nお前らの言葉を否定できる立場にないな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_00629",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "あ……ありがとうございます！　ヘルトさんに\n心から認めてもらえるよう、誠心誠意励みます……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00630",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "なら、私からもとりあえずはよし！\n……てか、ザスキアとアウグストは今どこにいるの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00631",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "知らん。俺とゼロを起こして、\nまたどこかに行ってしまった",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_00632",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "今回の任務は錬金術士レスナの監視および\n兄弟たちの統括……手段は任せると言い残してな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_00633",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "ま、ヘルトは他人の動向に興味のない人だし、\nそんなことだろうとは思ったけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_00634",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "「九偉人図」は？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00635",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "……これだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_00636",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "よっし、確かに２枚ね。\n約束通り、勝ったんだからもらっていくわよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00637",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "あら？　こっちにもう１枚あったわよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00638",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "全部で３枚……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00639",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 39,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "こいつらが持ってる「九偉人図」、２枚だったんじゃ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00640",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 40,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "あれは嘘だ。\n１枚は、隠し持っておくつもりだった",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_00641",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 41,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "切り札は隠し持っておいたほうが、\nゆさぶるのに都合がいいし、面白いしね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_00642",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 42,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "3986021654722714881",
		"text": "それには同意するけど、趣味悪いっての……\nって、シトリンはどっち目線なんだい！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00643",
		"still_path_hash": "4227931788932007159",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 43,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "にしても、それを素直にネタバラシするなんて……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00644",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 44,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "……そんな気分ではなくなっただけだ。\n持っていけ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_00645",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 45,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "3986021654722714881",
		"text": "……ま、もらえるものはありがたく頂戴いたしやす！\nこれで残りは１枚！　頑張った甲斐があった！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00646",
		"still_path_hash": "4227931788932007159",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 46,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "さて、あとはこの二人の身柄だが……\n諸島同盟がこいつらを拘束するのは、正直難しいな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_037_00647",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 47,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "ここは王国に任せて。凶悪犯の収容には定評があるよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00648",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 48,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "騎士団の誇りにかけて、しっかりと預かるよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_037_00649",
